/ * **xlib** - X Window System rendering using XLib

defs.name: IoError
defs.value:
pub enum IoError {

    #[error("Cairo error: {0}")]
    Cairo(
          #[from]
          Error),

    #[error("IO error: {0}")]
    Io(
       #[from]
       io::Error),
}

defs.name: BorrowError

pub enum BorrowError {

    #[error("Failed to borrow with Cairo error: {0}")]

    NonExclusive,
}
